## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources accessed. Some sources may not provide comprehensive insights into all demographic groups or global perspectives. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of technology means that findings may quickly become outdated. Further research could expand on these findings by incorporating more diverse and up-to-date sources.